label: AL rdfs:label@en
definition: AL definition@en
editor note: A IAO:0000116 SPLIT=|

label: building material
definition: A material entity used to build a dwelling or part of a dwelling.

label: roof material
definition: A building material used in the construction of a roof.

label: floor material
definition: A building material used in the construction of a floor

label: wall material
definition: A building material used in the construction of a wall.

label: numerical household wealth index
definition: A data item of a household's cumulative living standard represented in a numerical datum. The wealth index is calculated using easy-to-collect data on a household's ownership of selected assets, such as televisions and bicycles; materials used for housing construction; and types of water access and sanitation facilities.

label: air brick
definition: A brick with holes which is embedded in a wall to allow ventilation through it.

label: number of residents in a dwelling
definition: A scalar measurements datum of resident in a dwelling.

label: cooking fuel material
definition: A material entity that consists of fuel mainly used for cooking.

label: number of rooms for sleeping in a dwelling
alternative label: number of bedrooms in a dwelling
definition: number of rooms in a dwelling that are used for sleeping.

label: land area measurement datum
definition: A scalar measurement datum of land such as land owned by a household.

label: number of meals per day
definition: A scalar measurement datum of meals per day in a household

label: number of days per week eating meat
definition: A scalar measurement datum of days eating meat in a  week in a household

label: frequency of not satisfying food needs
definition: A categorical measurement datum that specifies how frequently the food needs of a household were not met.

label: glucose 6 phosphate dehydrogenase genotype
definition: A genotype information which is about the presence of certain genetic variants of glucose-6-phosphate dehydrogenase.

label: alpha thalassemia genotype
definition: A genotype information which is about the presence and degree of alpha-thalassemia, a form of thalassemia involving the number of functional HBA1 and HBA2 genes.

label: sickle hemoglobin genotype
definition: A genotype information which is about the presence of sickle-cell hemoglobin (HbS), an abnormal form of hemoglobin which is the oxygen-carrying protein within the red blood cells.

label: diagnosis of parasitic infectious disease
definition: A diagnosis that is an assertion that a patient has a parasitic infectious disease.

label: diagnosis of complicated malaria
definition: A diagnosis of malaria with the presence of any danger signs including inability to sit up or stand, vomiting everything, unable to breastfeed or drink and lethargy or meeting criteria for severe malaria.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, Grant Dorsey

label: diagnosis of severe malaria
definition: A diagnosis of complicated malaria based on WHO criteria that include the presence of parasite infections, most commonly P.falciparum, and any one or more of symptoms/signs of serious organ failures or abnormalities, including cerebral malaria, severe anemia, generalized convulsions, hypoglycemia, respiratory distress, fluid and electrolyte disturbances, acute renal failure, ARDS, circulatory collapse, abnormal bleeding, and Jaundice.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, Grant Dorsey

label: severe malaria symptom or sign information
definition: Symptom or sign information that is used for the diagnosis of severe malaria based on World Health Organization (WHO) criteria.

label: blood smear reading as positive or negative
definition: A categorical measurement datum that indicates the presence of asexual parasites in blood cells by microscopy using a value of positive or negative.

label: human participant under investigation
definition: a human being who bears a participant under investigation role

label: VEuPathDB alternative label
definition: An alternative label used in VEuPathDB project websites.

label: subcounty of Uganda
definition: A fourth-order administrative region of Uganda.

label: malaria medication
definition: A medication material intended to prevent or treat malaria.

label: non-malaria medication
definition: A medication material intended to prevent or treat a disease other than malaria.

label: household information
definition: An information content entity is about household.

label: diagnosis of symptomatic malaria
definition: A diagnosis of malaria based on positive blood smear with subjective fever or elevated temperature resulting in antimalarial treatment.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, Grant Dorsey

label: date of clinical visit
definition: A time measurement datum that specifies the date of a clinical visit.

label: asexual parasite density by microscope
definition: A scalar measurement datum that is the output of a microscopy assay on a specimen and is expressed as a ratio of asexual parasites to either the quantity of specimen or number of leukocytes within it.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, John Judkins

label: household identifier
definition: A symbol that denotes a specific household.

label: human study subject identifier
definition: A symbol that denotes a specific human participant under investigation.

label: study participant information
definition: An information content entity which is about features of a human participant under investigation.

label: febrile
definition: elevated temperature or subjective fever

label: subjective fever
definition: A phenotypic abnormality of a subjective fever as reported by the study participant or their parent/guardian
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, Grant Dorsey

label: participant under investigation
definition: an organism that is the bearer of a partipant under investigation role

label: building material role
definition: A role that inheres in a material entity that is realized in a building process in which the material entity will become part of a structure with a roof and walls standing more or less permanently in one place.

label: roof material role
definition: A building material role that inheres in a material entity that is realized in a building process in which the material entity will become part of a roof.

label: wall material role
definition: A building material role that inheres in a material entity that is realized in a building process in which the material entity will become part of a wall.

label: floor material role
definition: A building material role that inheres in a material entity that is realized in a building process in which the material entity will become part of a floor.

label: average asexual parasite density of a participant with asymptomatic microscopic parasitemia
definition: An average value of asexual parasites counted per microliter of blood (i.e. malaria parasite density) across mulitiple clinical visits of a participant who was diagnosed with asymptomatic microscopic parasitemia.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, Shon cade, Grant Dorsey

label: average asexual parasite density of a participant with malaria
definition: An average value of asexual parasites counted per microliter of blood (i.e. malaria parasite density) across mulitiple clinical visits of a participant who was diagnosed with malaria.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, Shon cade, Grant Dorsey

label: average number of female Anopheles per night
definition: An average value of female Anopheles mosquitoes collected across multiple collections (e.g. from one or more households on a number of nights).
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, Shon cade, Grant Dorsey

label: average number of female Anopheles tested for sporozoite
definition: An average value of Anopheles mosquitoes tested for sporozoites across multiple collections (e.g. from a given household across CDC light trap collections) in a given period.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, Shon cade, Grant Dorsey

label: average number of sporozoite-positive female Anopheles
definition: An average value of sporozoite positive female Anopheles mosquitoes across multiple collections (e.g. from a given household over a number of nights of collections).
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, Shon cade, Grant Dorsey

label: average percent of female Anopheles with Plasmodium sporozoites
definition: An average percentage value of female Anopheles mosquitoes tested as sporozoites-positive in all female mosquitoes tested for sporozoites across multiple collections.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, Shon cade, Grant Dorsey

label: number of clinical visits
definition: A data item of the total number of clinical visits by a participant in an investigation.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, Shon cade, Grant Dorsey

label: number of clinical visits resulting in a malaria diagnosis
definition: A data item of the number of clinical visits during which the participant was diagnosed with malaria
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, Shon cade, Grant Dorsey

label: number of clinical visits resulting in an asymptomatic microscopic parasitemia diagnosis
definition: A data item of the number of clinical visits during which the participant was diagnosed with asymptomatic microscopic parasitemia.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, Shon cade, Grant Dorsey

label: peripheral blood mononuclear cell specimen
definition: A processed specimen that is extracted from whole blood using gradient centrifugation that separates the blood into a layer of peripheral blood mononuclear cell under the top layer of plasma. It contains lymphocytes, monocytes or macrophages that are critical components in the immune system.

label: number of Anopheles collections
definition: A count of Anopheles mosquitoes collections performed (e.g. from a given household) in a given period.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, Shon cade, Grant Dorsey

label: sum number of female Anopheles in a collection
definition: A sum value for all species of female Anopheles mosquitoes in a given collections.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, Shon cade, Grant Dorsey

label: sum number of female Anopheles funestus in a collection
definition: A sum value for all female Anopheles funestus mosquitoes in a given collections.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, Shon cade, Grant Dorsey

label: sum number of female Anopheles gambiae in a collection
definition: A sum value for all female Anopheles gambiae mosquitoes in a given collections.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, Shon cade, Grant Dorsey

label: duration of observation of study participant
definition: A time datum for the duration of a patients participation in an investigation.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, Shon cade, Grant Dorsey

label: average number of clinical visits per year
definition: An average value for the number of clinical visits of a patient based on calendar years
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, Shon cade, Grant Dorsey

label: average number of clinical visits with asymptomatic microscopic parasitemia diagnosis per year
definition: An average value for the number of clinical visits of a patient with asymptomatic microscopic parasitemia based on calendar years.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, Shon cade, Grant Dorsey

label: average number of clinical visits with malaria diagnosis per year
definition: An average value for the number of clinical visits of a patient with malaria based on calendar years
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, Shon cade, Grant Dorsey

label: categorical household wealth index
definition: A data item about a household's cumulative living standard represented in a categorical datum. The wealth index is calculated using data on a household's ownership of selected assets, such as televisions and bicycles; materials used for housing construction; and types of water access and sanitation facilities.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: household asset information
definition: An information content entity about items that a household owns such as a car, funiture, etc.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: date of death
definition: A time measurement datum specifying the date of death
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: date of participant first enrolled in a study
definition: A time measurement datum that specified the date of participant first enrolled in a study
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: date of participant last seen in a study
definition: A time measurement datum that specified the date of participant last seen in a study
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: duration of abdominal pain
definition: A time measurement datum that measures the duration of having abdominal pain.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: duration of anorexia
definition: A time measurement datum that measures the duration of having anorexia.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: duration of cough
definition: A time measurement datum that measures the duration of having a cough.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: duration of diarrhea
definition: A time measurement datum that measures the duration of having diarrhea.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: duration of fatigue
definition: A time measurement datum that measures the duration of having fatigue.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: duration of headache
definition: A time measurement datum that measures the duration of having a headache.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: duration of jaundice
definition: A time measurement datum that measures the duration of having jaundice.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: duration of joint pains
definition: A time measurement datum that measures the duration of having joint pains.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: duration of muscle aches
definition: A time measurement datum that measures the duration of having muscle aches.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: duration of seizures
definition: A time measurement datum that measures the duration of having seizures.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: duration of subjective fever
definition: A time measurement datum that measures the duration of having subjective fever.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: duration of vomiting
definition: A time measurement datum that measures the duration of having vomiting.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: indicator of household having animal-drawn cart
definition: A household asset information indicating whether a member of a household has or owns an animal-drawn cart.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey, John Judkins

label: indicator of household having bank account
definition: A household asset information indicating whether a member of a household has a bank account.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey, John Judkins

label: indicator of household having boat without a motor
definition: A household asset information indicating whether a member of a household has or owns a boat without a motor.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey, John Judkins

label: indicator of household having car
definition: A household asset information indicating whether a member of a household has or owns a car or truck.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey, John Judkins

label: indicator of household having motorboat
definition: A household asset information indicating whether a member of a household has or owns a boat with a motor.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey, John Judkins

label: indicator of household having watch
definition: A household asset information indicating whether a member of a household has or owns a watch.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey, John Judkins

label: duration of study participation from enrollment to current visit
definition: A time measurement datum of the interval from participant enrollment in a study until the current visit.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey, John Judkins

label: number of fed female Anopheles funestus in a collection
definition: A measurement datum of the number of female Anopheles funestus with a recent blood meal in a given collection
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: number of fed female Anopheles gambiae in a collection
definition: A measurement datum of the number of female Anopheles gambiae with a recent blood meal in a given collection
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: number of female Anopheles dissected for parity in a collection
definition: A measurement datum of the number of female Anopheles dissected for parity in a given collection.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: number of female null parous Anopheles in a collection
definition: A measurement datum of the number of female Anopheles that have never layed eggs in a given collection.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: number of female parous Anopheles in a collection
definition: A measurement datum of the number of female Anopheles that have layed eggs before or are pregnant in a given collection.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: number of gravid or semi-gravid Anopheles funestus in a collection
definition: A measurement datum of the number of gravid or semi-gravid female Anopheles funestus in a given collection
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: number of gravid or semi-gravid female Anopheles gambiae in a collection
definition: A measurement datum of the number of gravid or semi-gravid female Anopheles gambiae in a given collection
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: number of non-gambiae or funestus female Anopheles species in a collection
definition: A measurement datum of the number of female Anopheles that are not gambiae nor funestus in a given collection.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: number of sleeping places in dwelling with a household
definition: A data item of the number of sleeping spaces in a dwelling.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: number of unassessable Anopheles funestus in a collection
definition: A measurement datum of the number of Anopheles funestus that could not be accessed in a given collection
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: number of unassessable Anopheles gambiae in a collection
definition: A measurement datum of the number of Anopheles gambiae that could not be assessed in a given collection
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: number of unfed female Anopheles funestus in a collection
definition: A measurement datum of the number of female Anopheles funestus without a recent blood meal in a given collection
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: number of unfed female Anopheles gambiae in a collection
definition: A measurement datum of the number of female Anopheles gambiae without a recent blood meal in a given collection
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: presence of Plasmodium gametocyte in blood by microscopy assay
definition: A Plasmodium gametocytes in blood by microscopy assay datum that specifies whether gametocytes were detected.
term editor: Person: Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey, John Judkins
parent class: Plasmodium gametocytes in blood by microscopy assay datum

label: reason for participant withdrawal
definition: An information content entity indicating the reason why a participant withdrew from a study.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: severe anemia
definition: An anemia with hemoglobin levels less than 5 gm/dL.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: slept in an insecticide treated net last night information
definition: An information content entity indicating whether a person slept in an insecticide treated net the previous night.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: sum number of female Anopheles examined for sporozoites in a collection
definition: A sum value for all female Anopheles examined for sporozoites in a given collection.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: sum number of female Anopheles with Plasmodium sporozoites in a collection
definition: A sum value for all female Anopheles with Plasmodium sporozoites in a given collection.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey

label: indicator of enrollment timing
definition: An information content entity indicating whether enrollment of a human study subject occurred at the beginning of a study or during the study.
term editor: Person:  Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, David Roos, Grant Dorsey, John Judkins

label: drinking water from pipe into dwelling
definition: drinking water accessed through a plumbing fixture located inside a human dwelling

label: drinking water from pipe into yard
definition: drinking water obtained through a plumbing fixture located in the yard of a human dwelling

label: display order
definition: An annotation property used to specify the order of terms displayed on a website.

label: parasite clearance half life
definition: half life datum (t 1/2) for cleaning parasite

label: parasite clearance rate
definition: a rate measurement datum that represents the number of parasite organisms removed from the bearer of a host role by means of the biological processes of the bearer of the host role

label: duration of parasite clearance
definition: a time measurement datum that is the result of measuring the time it takes for the biological processes of the bearer of a host role to remove parasite organisms within it, until such time as the organisms cannot be detected

label: haplogroup
definition: A population of people who share a common ancestor on the patrilineal or matrilineal line.

label: time parasitemia started
definition: a time measurement datum that represents the beginning of the first process in which a parasitemia is realized

label: treatment outcome information
definition: an information content entity that describes the success, failure, or indeterminacy of a treatment

label: information on dwelling facilities
definition: an information content entity that is about a process in which a human being occupying a dwelling participates. It either specifies the bearer of the function that is realized in the process, or it specifies that the process does not occur in the dwelling or its yard.

label: information on dwelling physical characteristics
definition: a information content entity that is about a part of a dwelling

label: socioeconomic factor
definition: an information content entity that is about a household and is an estimator of capabilities of household members to participate in processes that maintain their health, social status, and economic freedom

label: aggregated clinical visit information
definition: a data item that is about an investigation and is the specified output of a data transformation that has only clinical visit data as input

label: human genotype information
definition: a genotype information that is about the genetic material of a human being

label: information on participant study details
definition: an information content entity that is about a part of a study design execution that is part of an investigation under which a human being is a participant

label: hospitalization information
definition: an information content entity that is about a part of a health care encounter that occurs in a hospital facility

label: symptom or sign information
definition: an information content entity that is about a sign or symptom of a patient
editor note: This should stay consistent w/OGMS's definitions, so this definition may need to be changed if OGMS changes their definitions of sign and symptom to information content entities.

label: information on observation details
definition: an information content entity that is about a clinical visit

label: clinical visit type information
definition: an information content entity that specifies whether a clinical visit is scheduled or unscheduled

label: aggregated entomological data item
definition: an entomological data item that results from either (a) counting insect collections from multiple catches of live specimens or (b) an averaging data transformation that has single catch entomological measurement data as input

label: diagnosis of disease other than malaria
definition: A diagnosis that is an assertion that a patient, who is the subject of a diagnostic process, has a disease other than malaria.

label: hospital admission information
definition: an information content entity that is about a participant under investigation and specifies the hospital admitting the participant

label: date of hospital admission
definition: a time measurement datum that is about a human being who bears a patient role and specifies the date of the patient's admission to a hospital

label: date of hospital discharge
definition: a time measurement datum that is about a human being who bears a patient role and specifies the date of the patient's discharge from a hospital

label: diagnosis at patient discharge
definition: A diagnosis that is documented during the patient discharge process.

label: Anopheles funestus related information
definition: an information content entity that is about a collection of Anopheles funestus

label: Anopheles gambiae sensu lato related information
definition: an information content entity that is about a collection of Anopheles gambiae sensu lato

label: mosquito parity information
definition: an information content entity that is about a number of mosquitos that have given birth

label: sporozoite testing information
definition: an entomological data item that is the specified output of an analyte assay to determine whether a sporozoite is present in any insect in a collection of insects

label: aggregated sporozoite testing information
definition: a data item that is the specified output of a data transformation that has only sporozoite testing information as input

label: human waste disposal in a household
definition: A human waste disposal in a household.
parent class: information on disposal of human excreta material

label: number of non-scheduled visits
definition: A count of the total number of non-scheduled clinical visits in an investigation.

label: number of scheduled visits
definition: A count of the total number of scheduled clinical visits in an investigation.

label: information on malaria diagnosis and parasite status
definition: An information content entity that is about malaria diagnosis and parasite status testing by blood smear or LAMP.
term editor: Person: Jie Zheng, Grant Dorsey, John Judkins
editor note:
Values for this class:

Symptomatic malaria
Blood smear positive, no malaria
Blood smear negative, LAMP positive
Blood smear negative, LAMP negative
Blood smear negative, LAMP not done
Blood smear indicated but not done
Blood smear not indicated

label: vector control intervention information
definition: An information content entity that is about vector control intervention towards interruption of transmission of infectious diseases.

label: employment information
definition: An information content entity that is about employment.

label: domesticated animal in a human dwelling
definition: An organism that raised by people and lives in a human dwelling.

label: information on when bed net last treated
definition: An information content entity that is about when the bed net is last treated.

label: number of infections with P. vivax in lifetime
definition: A count of the total times of a person who infected with P. vivax in his lifetime.

label: number of infections with P. vivax in the last year
definition: A count of the total times of a person who infected with P. vivax last year.

label: number of infections with P. falciparum in lifetime
definition: A count of the total times of a person who infected with P. falciparum in his lifetime.

label: number of infections with P. falciparum in the last year
definition: A count of the total times of a person who infected with P. falciparum last year.

label: days per week at primary occupation
definition: A measurement datum of days per week spent in one's primary occupation.

label: days per week at secondary occupation
definition: A measurement datum of days per week spent in one's secondary occupation.

label: secondary occupation
definition: An occupation that a person is not involved in primarily.

label: secondary economic activity in last month
definition: An information content entity about secondary economic activity a person participates in the last month.

label: occupation
definition: An information content entity that is about an activity that realizes a social role and is often performed for payment.

label: primary economic activity pay period
definition: A time measurement datum about the pay period of primary economic activity.

label: secondary economic activity pay period
definition: A time measurement datum about the pay period of secondary economic activity.

label: indicator of whether person received payment from primary economic activity
definition: An information content entity about whether a person received payment from primary economic activity.

label: indicator of whether person received payment from secondary economic activity
definition: An information content entity about whether a person received payment from secondary economic activity.

label: salary of primary economic activity
definition: A data item of salary of primary job.

label: salary of secondary economic activity
definition: A data item of salary of other job.

label: hours per day at primary occupation
definition: A measurement datum of hours in one's primary occupation per day spent in that occupation.

label: hours per day at secondary occupation
definition: A measurement datum of hours in one's secondary occupation per day spent in that occupation.

label: marital status
definition: a categorical value specification that is about a human being and specifies whether that human being is joined to another human being in marriage

label: indicator of whether person plans to move
definition: a categorical value specification that specifies whether a human being plans to change within two years the dwelling which that human being occupies

label: relationship to head of household
definition: An information content entity that specifies the relationship between a person and the head of their household.

label: duration of residence in dwelling
definition: a time measurement datum that represents the time a human being resides in a human dwelling

label: duration of residence in community
definition: A time measurement datum of the time interval that a human being has lived in a geographic location where the inhabitants share a common trait.

label: number of common areas in a dwelling
definition: a count of the number of instances of a site, within a human dwelling and its yard, to which any resident of the dwelling has access

label: covered area measured in square meter
definition: a scalar measurement datum that has the square meter as its measurement label and is the result of a measurement of area that is covered by a roof

label: information on kitchen location
definition: An information content entity about where the kitchen is located inside or outside of a dwelling.

label: area measurement datum
definition: A scalar measurement datum that is the result of a measurement of area.

label: information on whether occupant owns or pays rent on dwelling
definition: a categorical value specification that is about a dwelling and specifies whether (a) it is owned by an occupant of the dwelling or (b) a rental agreement exists such that an occupant has an obligation to pay rent to someone who does not occupy the dwelling

label: information on travel in the last month
definition: An information content entity about travel to any place more than 10 km away from where a person lives.

label: information on travel before malaria
definition: an information content entity that is about a patient diagnosed with malaria and describes geographic locations the patient visited

label: bed net material
definition: A material entity that is used to make bed net.

label: date of last fumigation
definition: a time measurement datum that is about a human dwelling and specifies the most recent date on which the dwelling was fumigated, i.e. filled with pesticide

label: information on organization responsible for treating bed nets
definition: an information content entity that specifies the organization that administers insecticide to a collection of bed nets

label: information on contact with malaria
definition: An information content entity that specifies whether a human participant under investigation is a contact for malaria, based on the partipant's association with sites in which malaria infections are known to occur.

label: number of livestock
definition: a count of the number of instances of a domesticated animal that is raised in an agricultural setting to produce labor and commodities

label: number of pets
definition: a count of the number of instances of a domesticated animal that is kept for pleasure rather than utility

label: number of insecticide-treated bed nets treated less than 6 months ago
definition: a count of the number of instances of a bed net to which insecticide was applied in the past six months

label: cluster of differentiation 36 genotype
definition: A genotype information which is about  cluster of differentiation 36 (CD36) gene, which encodes an integral membrane protein in many cell types and a member of the scavenger receptor family that imports fatty acids into cells (Canton et al., 2013). CD36 is also an endothelial receptor for binding of erythrocytes infected with P. falciparum.
editor note:
Grant Dorsey: The human CD36 antigen is an integral membrane protein in many cell types and a member of the scavenger receptor family that imports fatty acids into cells (Canton et al., 2013). CD36 is also an endothelial receptor for binding of erythrocytes infected with P. falciparum; this cytoadhesion is believed to be an important feature of the virulence of falciparum malaria, due both to its prevention of clearance of infected erythrocytes by the spleen and to local effects of cytoadhering parasites (Newbold et al., 1999). Importantly, expression of CD36 is low in the brain, even in the setting of cerebral malaria (Silamut et al., 1999), suggesting that binding to CD36 is most relevant in non-cerebral forms of severe malaria. CD36 is also believed to be an important macrophage pattern recognition receptor that mediates innate recognition and clearance of infected erythrocytes (Cabrera et al., 2014). Considering our current understanding, CD36 expression might be seen to contribute to malaria severity, by mediating cytoadherence, or to help control malaria, via immune effects. Results with murine malaria models have been complex; mice with decreased CD36-mediated cytoadherence had decreased growth of P. berghei (Fonager et al., 2012), but CD36-deficient mice had increased risk of fatal P. chabaudi malaria (Patel et al., 2007). Considering human populations, many CD36 polymorphisms, including nonsense mutations that prevent production of the molecule, are common, particularly in African populations (Aitman et al., 2000). However, attempts to identify associations between common polymorphisms and malaria risk have led to inconsistent results, with evidence for enhancement of(Aitman et al., 2000; Omi et al., 2002), no effect (Fry et al., 2009), or protection from (Das et al., 2009; Omi et al., 2003; Pain et al., 2001; Sinha et al., 2008) severe malaria with different polymorphisms.
CD3T188G is a polymophism on the human CD36 gene.

label: term type
definition:
An annotation that specifies how a term is used in generation search filters on a website. It has five options:

category: a term to organize the variables for exploration on the website

variable: a variable in the dataset

variable, derived: one term that is calculated, using the data in two or more other variables

multifilter: any value below it in the hierarchy will be displayed as a multifilter

value: the value of a multifilter

label: default display range max
definition: Annotation property that specifies the default maximum value for each term's range. Useful to ensure that histograms for related terms have the same x-axis range

label: default bin width
definition: Annotation property that specifies the bin width for each term's histogram.

definition: Annotation property used to annotate numeric terms as strings. Numeric terms annotated as strings will ALWAYS be ordinal. Study specific.

label: metagenome pathway and function analysis
definition: A data transformation of metagenome input sequence data involving mapping to genes with full Enzyme Commision (EC) number enzyme classifications and calculation of pathways.

label: 4th level EC metagenome abundance data

label: metagenome enzyme pathway coverage data
definition: A data item that is the output of a metagenome pathway and function analysis for gene coverage in a pathway defined by EC classifications.

label: relative taxonomic abundance analysis
definition: A data transformation of input sequence data to obtain the fraction of relative abundance of organisms.

label: relative abundance of kingdom data

label: relative abundance of phylum data

definition: A data item that is the output of a relative taxonomic abundance analysis for organisms grouped at the level of family.

label: relative abundance of genus data
definition: A data item that is the output of a relative taxonomic abundance analysis for organisms grouped at the level of genus.

label: relative abundance of species data
definition: A data item that is the output of a relative taxonomic abundance analysis for organisms grouped at the level of species.

label: alpha diversity taxonomic analysis
definition: A data transformation of input sequence data to obtain a mean species diversity.

definition source: EuPathDB, based on definition for 'sign' in OGMS

label: indicator of whether participant has symptom

label: number of copies of the 2La Anopheles gambiae complex chromosomal inversion
definition: A count of the number of copies of the interspecific chromosomal inversion (2La) in Anopheles gambiae complex.
editor note: 2La is located on chromosome arm 2L:20524058-42165532 (approximate location in the AgamP3 assembly; GenBank: GCF_000005575.2) as described in: Sharakhov, I.V., White, B.J., Sharakhova, M.V., Kayondo, J., Lobo, N.F., Santolamazza, F., Della Torre, A., Simard, F., Collins, F.H. and Besansky, N.J., 2006. Breakpoint structure reveals the unique origin of an interspecific chromosomal inversion (2La) in the Anopheles gambiae complex. Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences, 103(16), pp.6258-6262. PMID: 16606844

label: number of copies of the 2Rb Anopheles gambiae complex chromosomal inversion
definition: A measurement datum of the number of copies of the chromosomal inversion 2Rb in Anopheles gambiae.
editor note: 2Rb is located on chromosome arm 2R:19023925-26758676 (location in the AgamP3 assembly; GenBank: GCF_000005575.2) as described in: Lobo, N.F., Sangar, D.M., Regier, A.A., Reidenbach, K.R., Bretz, D.A., Sharakhova, M.V., Emrich, S.J., Traore, S.F., Costantini, C., Besansky, N.J. and Collins, F.H., 2010. Breakpoint structure of the Anopheles gambiae 2R b chromosomal inversion. Malaria journal, 9(1), pp.1-9. PMID:20974007

label: number of copies of the 2Rc Anopheles gambiae complex chromosomal inversion
definition: A count of the number of copies of the trans-specific inversion 2Rc in Anopheles gambiae.
editor note: 2Rc is located on chromosome arm 2R:26780000-31450000 (location in the AgamP3 assembly; GenBank: GCF_000005575.2) as described in: White, B.J., Cheng, C., Sangar, D., Lobo, N.F., Collins, F.H. and Besansky, N.J., 2009. The population genomics of trans-specific inversion polymorphisms in Anopheles gambiae. Genetics, 183(1), pp.275-288. PMID:19581444

label: number of copies of the 2Rd Anopheles gambiae complex chromosomal inversion
definition: A count of the number of copies of the chromosomal inversion 2Rd in Anopheles gambiae.
editor note: 2Rd is located on chromosome arm 2R:31480000-42600000 (location in the AgamP3 assembly; GenBank: GCF_000005575.2) as described in: George, P., Sharakhova, M.V. and Sharakhov, I.V., 2010. Highresolution cytogenetic map for the African malaria vector Anopheles gambiae. Insect molecular biology, 19(5), pp.675-682. PMID:20609021

label: number of copies of the 2Rj Anopheles gambiae complex chromosomal inversion

Segmental Duplication Implicated in the Genesis of Inversion 2 Rj of Anopheles gambiae. PLoS One, 2(9), p.e849. PMID:17786220

label: number of copies of the 2Rk Anopheles gambiae complex chromosomal inversion

editor note: 2Rk is described in: Mario Coluzzi, Adriana Sabatini, Alessandra della Torre, Maria Angela Di Deco, Vincenzo Petrarca. A polytene chromosome analysis of the Anopheles gambiae species complex. PMID: 12364623

label: number of copies of the 2Ru Anopheles gambiae complex chromosomal inversion

The population genomics of trans-specific inversion polymorphisms in Anopheles gambiae. Genetics, 183(1), pp.275-288. PMID:19581444

definition: A female insect feeding status of having a visible blood meal.

definition: An organization that monitors mosquito species in the Florida Keys district, performs abatement, and is located in the Florida Keys, Florida, USA.

label: prevalence of Cyp4J5 L43F
definition: A data item that is the output of an assay to quantify the frequency of the genetic variation resulting in cytochrome P450 CYP4J5 L43F associated with pyrethroid resistance and located in the 2La inversion of Anopheles gambiae.

label: Lurex attractor
definition: An arthropod attractor that is manufactured by the American Biophysics Corporation and has (S)-lactic acid as its active ingredient in order to mimic the scent of human skin.

label: tick specimen collection process by citizen scientists
definition: An arthropod specimen collection process in which tick specimens are collected by the general public i.e., citizen scientists.

label: geolocation provision information
definition: Geolocation provenance information that specifies that data were provided directly from a source, rather than estimated or calculated.

label: geolocation obfuscation information
definition: Geolocation provenance information that specifies that the number of decimal places in the data were truncated.

label: geolocation estimation information from curator
definition: Geolocation provenance information that specifies that data were calculated by the curator or found using a geolocation lookup service.

label: geolocation estimation from administrative region information
definition: Geolocation provenance information that specifies that data were estimated using information about an administrative region.
editor note: Usually this means an arbitrary or centroid location within that country, or the results of a geocoding service.

label: geolocation data estimation information from first- or higher-order administrative region
definition: Geolocation provenance information that specifies that data were estimated from information about an administrative region of first order or higher.
parent class: geolocation estimation from administrative region information

label: geolocation estimation information from second- or higher-order administrative region
definition: Geolocation provenance information that specifies that data were estimated from from information about an administrative region of second order or higher.
parent class: geolocation data estimation information from first- or higher-order administrative region

label: geolocation estimation information from street address or landmark
definition: Geolocation provenance information that specifies that data were estimated from a street address or landmark.
editor note: Usually this will be the result of a geocoding service.
parent class: geolocation estimation information from second- or higher-order administrative region

label: information on putatively essential gene
definition: A conclusion based on data about a gene that is absolutely necessary or vital for the life of an organism, as inferred either from direct experimental evidence or from indirect evidence.

label: prevalence of wild type Cyp4J5 L43
definition: A data item that is the output of an assay to quantify the frequency of the reference sequence amino acid at Cyp4J5 L43 or is calculated from data items of the frequency of a variant at that position.

label: Anopheles nuneztovari sensu lato
editor note: This species is not in NCBITaxon so is assigned a EUPATH ID.

label: Anaplasma phagocytophilum str. Ap-ha
editor note: This species is not in NCBITaxon so is assigned a EUPATH ID.

label: Anaplasma phagocytophilum str. Ap-v1
editor note: This species is not in NCBITaxon so is assigned a EUPATH ID.

label: umbilical cord blood specimen collection process
definition: A collecting specimen from organism that has the objective to obtain an umbilical cord blood specimen.

label: blood hydroxychloroquine concentration
definition: A blood assay datum of the concentration of hydroxychloroquine.

label: presence of Severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 in nasopharynx or oropharynx by real time reverse-transcription polymerase chain reaction assay
definition: A virus in nasopharyngeal or oropharyngeal swab datum that specifies whether severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 was detected by real time reverse-transcription polymerase chain reaction assay.
parent class: virus in nasopharyngeal or oropharyngeal swab datum

label: district of Uganda
definition: A second-order administrative region of Uganda.

label: region of Uganda
definition: A first-order administrative region of Uganda.

label: maternal saliva assay
definition: A saliva assay that evaulates a specimen collected from the biological mother of an infant.

label: ward of Tanzania
definition: A fourth-order administrative region of Tanzania.

label: presence of Mycobacterium tuberculosis in cerebrospinal fluid by polymerase chain reaction assay
definition: A cerebrospinal fluid microbiology datum that specifies whether Mycobacterium tuberculosis was detected.

label: presence of Histoplasma capsulatum in urine by polymerase chain reaction assay
definition: A eukaryota in urine datum that specifies whether Histoplasma capsulatum was detected by polymerase chain reaction assay.

label: presence of bacteria in cerebrospinal fluid
definition: A cerebrospinal fluid microbiology datum that specifies whether bacteria were detected.

label: presence of bacteria in urine
definition: A urine microbiology datum that specifies whether bacteria were detected.

label: presence of Cryptococcus in blood
definition: A eukaryota in blood datum that specifies whether Cryptococcus was detected.

label: presence of Cryptococcus in cerebrospinal fluid
definition: A cerebrospinal fluid microbiology datum that specifies whether Cryptococcus was detected.

label: presence of eukaryote in cerebrospinal fluid
definition: A cerebrospinal fluid microbiology datum that specifies whether a eukaryote was detected.

label: presence of Histoplasma in blood
definition: A eukaryota in blood datum that specifies whether Histoplasma was detected.

label: presence of Histoplasma in cerebrospinal fluid
definition: A cerebrospinal fluid microbiology datum that specifies whether Histoplasma was detected.

label: presence of Histoplasma in urine
definition: A eukaryota in urine datum that specifies whether Histoplasma was detected.

label: presence of Mycobacterium in blood
definition: A bacteria in blood datum that specifies whether Mycobacterium was detected.

label: presence of Mycobacterium in cerebrospinal fluid
definition: A cerebrospinal fluid microbiology datum that specifies whether Mycobacterium was detected.

label: presence of Mycobacterium in urine
definition: A urine microbiology datum that specifies whether Mycobacterium was detected.

label: Shigella flexneri not 7 in feces datum
definition: A bacteria in feces datum that is used to determine the presence of Shigella flexneri that is not serotype 7 in the specimen.
